            Tools For Life Workshop Slides
          Heading link



 
Copy link



Just as college prepares you for your future career this workshop prepares you for Life.  View our slides to gain knowledge on the top life areas that will help you to make better day-to-day decisions. Topics covered in this workshop include: street safety, saving made easy, healthy eating on the run, managing your first apartment, dealing with roommates, shopping on a budget, finding a job, smoother life transitions, and more.


      Click here to view workshop slides!
    










